{"word":"H2616 - חָסַד - châçad - khaw-sad' - Shew self merciful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָסַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châçad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-sad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Shew self merciful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவமானத்தோடிரு, தயவுள்ள வராயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to be good, to be kind; (Hithpael) to show kindness to oneself"},{"paragraph":"2) to be reproached, to be ashamed; (Piel) to be put to shame, to be reproached"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly perhaps to <i>bow</i> (the neck only (compare <a href=\"#/H2603 - חָנַן - chânan - khaw-nan'/2603\">H2603</a>) in courtesy to an equal), that is, to <i>be kind</i>; also (by euphemism (compare <a href=\"#/H1288 - בָרַךְ - bârak - baw-rak'/1288\">H1288</a>), but rarely) to <i>reprove: - </i>shew self merciful, put to shame."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2616 - חָסַד - châçad - khaw-sad'/2616\">H2616</a>, <a href=\"#/H2617 - חֵסֵד - chêçêd - kheh'-sed/2617\">H2617</a>, <a href=\"#/H2619 - חֲסַדְיָה - Chăçadyâh - khas-ad-yaw'/2619\">H2619</a>, <a href=\"#/H2623 - חָסִיד - châçîyd - khaw-seed'/2623\">H2623</a>, <a href=\"#/H2624 - חֲסִידָה - chăçîydâh - khas-ee-daw'/2624\">H2624</a>"}]}